## Knowledge Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Audit current knowledge: what exists, where it lives, gaps
- [ ] 2. Define knowledge categories and taxonomy
- [ ] 3. Identify knowledge owners and subject matter experts
- [ ] 4. Design the knowledge architecture (wiki, database, etc.)
- [ ] 5. Implement capture processes: templates, review cycles
- [ ] 6. Monitor usage and iterate

